This Logic App contains simple C# code which  has a HTTP POST API request triggered from POSTMAN 
it sends serialized JSON Data with three fields Item Type , Quanity and Price .
Logic App has  when HTTPS Request is Received Connector and once request is Received , it inserts the data into SQL table Sales Data 
 In Order to handle Exceptions , we have used Scope blocks and Insertion into Sales Data takes place when there is no Exception TRY BLOCK
 Catch Block Executes when when TRY block os not suceesful and it Set the Error Detail Variable and Inserts the row in Tbl Error Details 
